text: Matt or Matthew McCoy may refer to: * Matt McCoy (actor) (born 1958), American actor * Matt McCoy (American football) (born 1982), American football linebacker * Matt McCoy (politician) (born 1966), Iowa State Senator * Matt McCoy (worship leader), songwriter, worship leader and Christian musician * Matt McCoy (rugby league) (1923–2007), Australian rugby league footballer * Matthew McCoy (Magistrate) (1819–1853), Magistrate of the British Overseas Territory of Pitcairn Island, 1843 and 1853 * Matthew Edmond McCoy (1868–1929), Magistrate of the British Overseas Territory of Pitcairn Island, 1909
title: Matt McCoy
